data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-4 Bedroom brick home located conveniently to all your local amenities. As you explore this home, you'll discover its hidden treasures, including a recently remodeled bonus room in the basement that could serve as a private living space or in-law quarters. The lower level also boasts ample storage space, providing practicality and versatility. Step outside, and you'll find a spacious backyard, perfect for all your outdoor entertainment needs or as a play area for your kids, friends, or pets. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity. Ask us about the $5,000 grant available for this home to buy down the rate or use toward closing costs!
